summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fourth Avenue Northeast, from East Sixtieth Street to East Sixty-fifth Street in the City of Seattle by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 20369, creating Local Improvement District No. 1964 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
